works.title: templet-one
works.desc: Vörda (Swedish for “to protect, to respect”) is a US-based brand committed to bringing high-quality, natural products sourced from Asia and Europe to the North American market. By North was commissioned to develop the name, brand strategy, visual identity and packaging for the new brand. We developed a bespoke logotype with distinct features that comes to life in animations.
